      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver benchmarked against canonical internal flow problems; order-of-accuracy confirmed.",
      "rationale": "The Fluent solver was verified against the Taylor–Couette and lid-driven cavity benchmarks. Observed order of accuracy matched theoretical second-order expectation within 5%, satisfying Gradation 2."
