    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors met or exceeded their required gradation levels for MRL 2. Six factors were appropriately scoped out at MRL 2 for a Class II device. The central hemolysis claim is supported by a comprehensive body of work encompassing mesh convergence studies, turbulence model benchmarking, and experimental validation against the FDA GCBP interlaboratory dataset. The assessment team concludes that the CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility for the stated context of use and recommends acceptance for regulatory submission.",
